---
title: Smart Mini Beef Patties and Sesame-Miso Dressing with Spinach Slaw and Crispy Shallots
description: A rainbow of colours from an array of fresh veggies make this a gorgeous plate! It's also a healthy option for when you want something light that's still packed with flavour. The fragrant sesame-miso-dressed slaw is the real hero here!
